cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper is about Person Re-Identification (ReID) using a modified softmax function to simultaneously solve the classification problem and learn a hypersphere manifold embedding. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a convolutional neural network and introduces a balanced sampling strategy, which could also make it relevant to Multimedia (cs.MM), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) sub-categories.
